handle EINTR in the test thread:

# git log -n 1 .
commit 4af3a7a23ff67d621a71f1a73ff8ea3f892a07d9
Author: ru <ru@FreeBSD.org>
Date:   Thu Feb 25 14:42:26 2010 +0000

    Fixed missing or broken library dependencies.

